  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b9e\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two youths arrested for cutting old man's chain in Vavunia",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police of Vavunia Crime Prevention Division said that two youths were arrested yesterday (05) in Vavunia.",
        "Last week, an old man was traveling on a two-wheeler in Vavunia, Thenikal area when two youths who were following him on a motorcycle cut the chain he was wearing.",
        "In this regard, the elderly victim had lodged a complaint with the Vavuniya Crime Prevention Division police. The police investigated the complaint and arrested two youths aged 33 and 25 from Vavunia, Dhonikal and Siriramapuram areas and recovered six half-pound chains from being pawned in a private financial institution on Bazaar Road.",
        "Further investigations have been carried out by the police and they have taken steps to produce the two persons in the court, they added."
      ],
